  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Let me-- in a-- in-- in a second.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What happened at Los Angeles was-- what happened in Los Angeles was two things.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Nazis published a nasty, mean article, just a full page type-- no, printed article about everything nasty that you or anybody can possibly think up and inserted copies of it in the As the copies came off the printing press-- you must remember at that time, the printed paper is much slower than they are doing nowadays.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is one thing that got the Jewish community excited.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Here they're reading, opening the That was one thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The other thing was they were concerned-- leaders of the Jewish community who were primarily looking after social welfare, they looked, made sure that there is a hospital where Jewish doctors can practice because it was not easy for Jewish doctors to get into a regular hospital.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They looked after the cemetery.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They helped the people who needed to adjust themselves, coming from Russia or anywhere else in Europe, but particularly Russia and places like that.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was called the Federation of Jewish Welfare Organizations at that time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, so they had a little bit of a headquarter, a place where they could eat weenies-- you know, with little Germans you would say weenies, hamburger, lots of beer, and so on, and so forth, and a place where they could do a little gymnastics.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that association or that federation had a regular election of officers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The local Nazis claimed that this is an organization that has the right to be in there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That this is an organization.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They faked-- they created fake organizations in order to have more delegates that could then elect their kind of people to be presidents and vice presidents in there.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
